{"tid":1713708,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"CU手足千奇唔好搞Lab 隨時成隊popo全軍覆滅","createTime":"2019-11-12T19:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T19:31:10.000Z","uid":301784,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c67f556174d3350418eb99f76fd9a1ccb1c78eed","tid":1713708,"uid":301784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:00:57.000Z","msg":"希望可以提下CU手足<br />\nCU入邊 Dept of chem 大大話話都有成廿個professor, 每個professor一間Lab嘅話都有廿幾間Lab<br />\nLab入邊應該都有唔少有毒/強腐蝕性/可燃性化學品<br />\n<br />\n有毒/強腐蝕性：<br />\n處理時一定要戴手套+Lab袍，如果直接接觸皮膚輕則可能紅種/敏感，重則可能會死亡（如Hydrofluoric acid），即使全身包到popo咁，都有機會奶野。只有消防HazMat嘅核生化保護袍先可以防護到。所以處理嘅時候要小心，自己定popo奶野都好難搞。如果高空擲物嘅話popo就難搞啦<br />\n<br />\n可燃性化學品<br />\n比較多喺有機溶劑，如 methanol/ ethanol/ ethyl acetate/ hexane/ benzene/ toluene 等等，做有機嘅應該清楚，有部份係汽油主要成份，處理嗰陣唔好聞到/吸入其蒸氣有害（但係幾乎都可以用豬嘴過濾），全部都燒得，一個Lab加埋 &gt;100 L 甚至到幾百公升都唔出奇<br />\n而且Lab入邊其實有好多炸藥嘅原材料，就好似TATP係用丙酮/雙氧水/鹽酸or硝酸制成，每間Lab幾乎都會有<br />\n再加上Lab入邊一定有大量嘅玻璃容器，有部份化學物質遇到空氣就會炸，所以將啲易爆化學品放入玻璃樽=手榴彈<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁樣做會好危險，但係當支槍殺到埋身準備打爆你個頭，只可以咁樣博一博<br />\n（From tg）"},{"pid":"27cedd56d27311bd7ebd562469cde6672508af1b","tid":1713708,"uid":155450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"0c16359d0ad53ddae788b21a9f948b3a173cfdd2","tid":1713708,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:03:18.000Z","msg":"火箭炮彈頭放呢d<br />\n用手扔唔遠"},{"pid":"762894e106c6ef08d15d97120bb49498f6afc2b5","tid":1713708,"uid":301784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:11:05.000Z","msg":"最好讀physic/chem/med嘅手足入去 同埋上gear預防危險品hi到<br />\n危險品Label<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqYgaSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqYgaSQ.jpg&h=7288d7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXrdXxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXrdXxR.jpg&h=e5282bf5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea0d02997a3f897953b133b2a8c50552e94453b9","tid":1713708,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-F30JwBRK7rI/WWsi2eIc2GI/AAAAAAAAASs/QRs1iYXrLoQ4asj6CNFVIBnSt8EuHbVjACLcBGAs/s1600/BmPJIbnIIAEWNTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-F30JwBRK7rI%2FWWsi2eIc2GI%2FAAAAAAAAASs%2FQRs1iYXrLoQ4asj6CNFVIBnSt8EuHbVjACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FBmPJIbnIIAEWNTK.jpg&h=dd355f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果跟到呢幾步做 就好大機會贏返少少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713666\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713666</a>"},{"pid":"0e1faac5cc95f123fc58e8eac248620a9eed565a","tid":1713708,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T19:31:10.000Z","msg":"嗱 我就完全唔支持手足咁做<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家千祈唔好咁定去狗堆到</span></span>"}]}